  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Tanzania - Water Sector Project: Increase human and physical capital and reduce the prevalence of water-related diseases by expanding the capacity of the Lower Ruvu Water Treatment Plant from 180 to 270 million liters per day; rehabilitating water intake and water treatment plants, and improving the existing distribution network in the city of Morogoro.</narrative>
  </description>
